Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.70,0:40:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.90,0:40:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什烦恼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:55.18,0:40:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近做什都不顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.42,0:41:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.58,0:41:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作一直失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.18,0:41:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没中奖过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.02,0:41:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是很容易被骂\N我到底该怎么做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:33.74,0:41:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此\N这些小事那么容易解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.90,0:41:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了\N马上帮您算一算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.22,0:42:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了\N原因在于你的戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.14,0:42:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒指吗\N是的 没了戒指运气就会好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.50,0:42:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连赌赛马都会赢钱喔\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.34,0:42:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错的\N卡片是这样指示的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.30,0:42:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点取掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.82,0:42:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了呢\N去掉它 运气就会变好唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.34,0:43:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟离婚的老婆的婚戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.46,0:43:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她还有情感在\N快点忘记前妻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.22,0:43:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忘记过去就无法有未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.94,0:43:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.74,0:43:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是优柔寡断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.74,0:43:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了\N我来你忘记前妻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.78,0:44:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干嘛 \N放心 我会帮助你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.54,0:44:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了会让你忘记前妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:43.02,0:44:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.62,0:45:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子有什么感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.30,0:45:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太方便耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.22,0:45:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多坏东西积在身体里喔\N我看到了 你最近都没做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.66,0:45:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了喔\N是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.34,0:46:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起来改运吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:19.50,0:46:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.26,0:46:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请想象一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.30,0:47:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.42,0:48:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你美好回忆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.30,0:49:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涨喔 不要忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:39.98,0:49:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要遮住\N很棒的宝贝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.78,0:50:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.30,0:51:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.22,0:51:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.82,0:55:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好奇妙喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:12.14,0:55:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢在改运了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:06.86,1:02:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:22.38,1:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次被这样吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:04.62,1:06:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:11.18,1:06:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像忘了前妻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:34.54,1:06:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 如此一来 运气会越来越好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:59.34,1:07:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.02,1:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟前妻离婚一定是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:12.94,1:07:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找下一位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:21.42,1:07:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人看起来太无趣了 不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:26.38,1:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过应该可以试看看\N瞒着家人去酒店
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:42.22,1:07:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个情报可以使用喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.30,1:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请喔 请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:56.94,1:08:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大喔 这里\N对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.82,1:08:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一下喔\N快好了 躺着吧 小心别滑倒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:28.62,1:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺这边 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:54.22,1:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你几岁呢 20岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:39.82,1:09:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人戒指可以脱掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:47.66,1:09:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N碰到会痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:56.94,1:10:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次有人说耶\N这戒指很重要 我怕弄丢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:05.90,1:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若一定要拿掉的话 我还是会配合
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:13.58,1:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 就戴着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:25.90,1:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊 你刚说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:35.18,1:10:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:39.82,1:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒指是谁送的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:46.70,1:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是啦\N那一定很贵吧 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.54,1:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔 我一定要弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:04.30,1:12:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一直舔手指了\N帮我吹好吗 不好意思 太喜欢乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:25.42,1:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用身体润滑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:44.14,1:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:02.38,1:14:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:53.26,1:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢 爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.22,1:16:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要摸我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:43.66,1:17:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欲求不满吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:01.42,1:19:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿如何呢 好爽喔\N脚很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:59.50,1:21:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大好爽喔\N真开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:59.34,1:22:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬硬的好爽喔\N顶到奶头好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:23.18,1:22:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先帮我吹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:11.98,1:23:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢 很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:39.98,1:24:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒越来越硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:29.74,1:25:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以干我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:56.62,1:33:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大力干我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:02.22,1:34:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:10.70,1:36:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面干我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:20.62,1:36:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要爽一点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:54.06,1:39:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你舔干净喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:31.66,1:40:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了 可以再一次吗\N还想再一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:47.50,1:40:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:42.86,1:43:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:46.70,1:43:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:52.14,1:44:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个什么\N我那么认真才拿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:04.30,1:44:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续加油\N总是会找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:10.38,1:44:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很烦耶\N别再命令我了别
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:25.26,1:44:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个呢\N要去咖啡厅才能找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:39.50,1:44:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:57.42,1:45:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他了 欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:04.94,1:45:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天麻美不在吗\N麻美吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:11.98,1:45:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在这工作的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:15.66,1:45:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚被我赶走的女生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:20.14,1:45:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:22.54,1:45:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天休假耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:27.50,1:45:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔 那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:35.66,1:45:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚有打电话来说今天还是来上班好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:47.02,1:45:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我等一下吧 \N好啊 请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:57.42,1:46:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 客人很麻美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:06.22,1:46:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一定要跟她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:11.34,1:46:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了这个来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:22.22,1:46:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会收下吗\N这个嘛 她说她有男友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:34.70,1:46:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 你不知道吗\N是喔 她有交往的对象喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:47.34,1:46:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 但别气馁 还有更多比她更好的女生喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:57.42,1:47:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:12.94,1:47:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢 欢迎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:23.82,1:47:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没人跟麻美一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:27.50,1:47:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别光看外表啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:34.06,1:47:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对自己还有自信 我不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:41.42,1:47:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:47.82,1:47:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:50.22,1:47:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被麻美看到就不好了\N她有男友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:54.86,1:48:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点放弃\N我们来做好玩的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:03.34,1:48:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你就会变心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:12.14,1:48:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我只喜欢麻美\N不要但是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:17.10,1:48:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天跟我玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:38.70,1:48:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管麻美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:54.06,1:50:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不好啦 为什么\N这样对麻美不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:01.89,1:50:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴这么说 但这边\N这样对麻美真不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:12.77,1:50:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟麻美说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:22.54,1:50:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬梆梆喔\N你很喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:42.38,1:50:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热喔 硬梆梆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:07.18,1:51:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要穿内裤了\N对不起 麻美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:19.50,1:51:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你常常都那么硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:47.50,1:52:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越大了\N一定忍很久了 射给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:24.14,1:52:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会痒吗 不行\N还想要吗 喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:35.66,1:52:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我这样玩吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:21.74,1:53:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不输麻美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:34.06,1:53:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要摸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:56.46,1:55:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸你的宝贝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:24.78,1:56:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美惠这样帮你吗\N不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:49.74,1:56:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:57.10,1:57:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:01.58,1:59:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美不会这样帮你喔\N跟我结婚就每天这样帮你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:12.78,2:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:25.74,2:00:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟麻美谁比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:40.30,2:00:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你吹喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:07.66,2:03:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越越爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:47.82,2:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你很爽的\N我忘你忘记麻美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:45.58,2:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就忘了麻美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:02.22,2:07:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:07.50,2:07:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢 变心了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:23.82,2:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我结婚\N好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:38.22,2:07:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 我会珍惜它的\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:44.46,2:07:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:49.74,2:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个吗\N可惜不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:07:55.98,2:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又错了吗\N名单里有犯人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:02.86,2:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:13.74,2:08:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续加油吧\N等一下老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:19.98,2:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难找喔\N最后是IP公同的桥本了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:32.30,2:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 截肢快出现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:45.74,2:08:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 有桥本的包裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:51.50,2:08:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N哪一位桥本呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:08:58.22,2:09:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有两位桥本呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:02.54,2:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是桥本
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:05.26,2:09:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有写桥本耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:10.86,2:09:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:22.70,2:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥本有两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:41.90,2:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 只好两位一起上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:48.14,2:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:09:53.58,2:09:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 好怪的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:27.66,2:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥本你再公司订这个 太夸张了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:37.58,2:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你订的吧 才不是我\N是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:47.34,2:10:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没订喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:52.62,2:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧\N不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:10:57.90,2:11:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不要的话 可以给我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:04.30,2:11:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:06.22,2:11:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我蛮想用看看的\N好啊 反正都寄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:29.26,2:11:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,震动好快喔 真可爱 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:11:38.54,2:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这个吗\N现在没男友很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:01.10,2:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:13:09.42,2:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:14:01.74,2:14:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:15:10.38,2:15:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我舔很爽吧 都很爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:14.22,2:19:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔 超爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:33.42,2:25:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我吹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:33:31.82,2:33:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也要 好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:34:49.42,2:34:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好性感喔 站着\N欲求不满吗 对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:35:12.46,2:35:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔 慢慢动喔\N好深喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:41:30.86,2:41:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己动喔\N我还想要吹肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:43:51.34,2:43:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这姿势好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:24.78,2:45:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:45:28.78,2:45:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:52:33.10,2:52:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要桥本射给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:55:31.18,2:55:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔干净喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:55:47.18,2:55:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁比较爽呢\N我吧 是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:55:58.06,2:56:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天平手\N下次再一起做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:16.14,2:56:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:21.90,2:56:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:24.62,2:56:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个吗 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:32.94,2:56:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表现太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:40.30,2:56:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:45.58,2:56:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老板要找这戒指呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:49.74,2:56:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的结婚戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:56:54.54,2:57:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板的吗\N是上次跟情妇去温泉旅行·
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:01.42,2:57:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果掉了 回去已经不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:09.58,2:57:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算找到了\N太太不会生气了 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:19.66,2:57:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:29.42,2:57:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太白痴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:33.58,2:57:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是重要的戒指 别乱丢啦\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:45.58,2:57:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易找到的戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:51.50,2:57:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也有爽到 就算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:57:58.54,2:58:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在无法停止追求性爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:06.05,2:58:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个目标是
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:16.94,2:58:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:21.74,2:58:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,END
